<HEADLINE>
FT  21 MAY 93 / Stock and Currency Markets
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
STOCK MARKET INDICES
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
FT-SE 100:                           2816.8              (-2.9)
