   By ROBERT GIBBENS
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
POWER Corp of Canada, with nearly CDollars 1bn (USDollars 700m) of cash and
short-term investments, is considering several new projects in the US, says
Mr Paul Desmarais, chairman.
In all, Power Corp and Pargesa, the jointly-owned European holding company,
have cash resources totalling CDollars 2.5bn and very low debt, Mr Desmarais
said.
