<HEADLINE>
FT  20 MAY 93 / Bristol plan
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
HANSON, the UK-US conglomerate, has announced plans to build a Pounds 30m
leisure and retail complex on the site of a former tobacco factory in
Bristol. The company expects to start work next year it wins planning
permission.
